{"id": "1411240188641939588", "channel_id": "1411240188641939588", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "想打375 或是新手為了融災向練角的也可以先看看 提前練角色\n吃練度和卡池深度\n我有壓練度可以按需要補上命輪或是去借角色\n以下會分享10個隊伍 會分享角色需要練到多少 需要找什麼造物 以及會有王關戰鬥影片\n有幫到大家的話 請幫我點個薯條🍟", "timestamp": "2025-08-30T06:44:40.547000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 19}, {"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411240188641939588", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全4級400融災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1395992069688004689", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1411240891573862420", "channel_id": "1411240188641939588", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "先說一下打4級需要注意的事情\n打4級會建議練好生存角色\n大多隊伍都是一帶三\n也有平均四隻都要練的 但相應的整體練度可以不用那麼高", "timestamp": "2025-08-30T06:47:28.139000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411240188641939588", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全4級400融災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1395992069688004689", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1411241391278915655", "channel_id": "1411240188641939588", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "先分析這期的關卡\n第一波要打米粒王 我建議是找生存高或爆發高的隊伍 並且進關就去打王", "timestamp": "2025-08-30T06:49:27.278000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-30T07:12:33.014000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411240188641939588", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全4級400融災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1395992069688004689", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1411241418533371995", "channel_id": "1411240188641939588", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2025-08-30T06:49:33.776000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1411241418235580446", "filename": "Screenshot_20250828_162953_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 174329, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411240188641939588/1411241418235580446/Screenshot_20250828_162953_Morimens.jpg?ex=69cc173d&is=69cac5bd&hm=75e066fa4b232c1dd28a5a332ff5a5c16e0436c5d3c53c08f5609e9e75102ac4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411240188641939588", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全4級400融災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1395992069688004689", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1411241452184404010", "channel_id": "1411240188641939588", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "https://youtu.be/EOPWaQfp-OA?si=6eyVCAOkeI8ri188", "timestamp": "2025-08-30T06:49:41.799000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "忘卻前夜 融災禁區_1-4 「海之使徒」珊 盾擊  #忘卻...", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EOPWaQfp-OA", "description": "#融災禁區 #忘卻前夜 #morimens"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411240188641939588", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全4級400融災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1395992069688004689", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1411244686668075060", "channel_id": "1411240188641939588", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "第一波是珊盾擊\n這隊平均練度高就可以了\n珊需要+4 全隊要點靈塑5級\n\n珊一定要帶 36室之環 堅韌意志\n第二件可以帶任意一件有死亡抵抗屬性的\n最優解會是 跨越疼痛\n\n諾締拉需要帶 遠方的歡宴 記憶螺旋\n第二件建議帶有盾量加成的\n最優解會是 不存在之地\n其次是 鏡中人 孤羽\n\n隊伍需要帶鑰令 短暫的永恆\n\n珊練度夠高可以嘗試1-5", "timestamp": "2025-08-30T07:02:32.960000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-30T10:16:11.875000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411240188641939588", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全4級400融災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1395992069688004689", "1181143392739147778"]}
