{"id": "1411244810081275985", "channel_id": "1411240188641939588", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "https://youtu.be/GM7dFIZVxbQ?si=ulJ0bWnWmg98FSKo", "timestamp": "2025-08-30T07:03:02.384000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "忘卻前夜 融災禁區_1-4 「海之使徒」血希羊媽  #忘...", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GM7dFIZVxbQ", "description": "#融災禁區 #忘卻前夜 #morimens"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411240188641939588", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全4級400融災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1395992069688004689", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1411246725246746725", "channel_id": "1411240188641939588", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "第一波額外是羊媽血希\n這隊要練 泰旖絲 和 血鏈·希洛\n隊伍點 泰旖絲 和 血鏈·希洛 的靈塑就足夠了\n\n血鏈·希洛一定要帶 四月禮讚 沉入殷紅\n第二件建議帶 掙脫鎖鏈之日 或 巨人之刃\n\n泰旖絲帶有銀鑰充能的裝備就可以\n最優解是 慈悲的哺育\n\n隊伍需要帶鑰令 唯一的種子", "timestamp": "2025-08-30T07:10:38.995000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411240188641939588", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全4級400融災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1395992069688004689", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1411249145498435684", "channel_id": "1411240188641939588", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "第二波打少校 因為有故人的懷錶+\n所以建議用生存高或可以打反擊的隊伍", "timestamp": "2025-08-30T07:20:16.028000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411240188641939588", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全4級400融災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1395992069688004689", "1181143392739147778"]}
