{"id": "1411256263534186516", "channel_id": "1411240188641939588", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "https://youtu.be/IaG50r7gDiQ?si=kfCSNo4m2getKgt3", "timestamp": "2025-08-30T07:48:33.100000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "忘卻前夜 融災禁區_2-4 少校 莉莉 #忘卻前夜 #morimens", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IaG50r7gDiQ", "description": "#融災禁區 #忘卻前夜 #morimens"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411240188641939588", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全4級400融災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1395992069688004689", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1411258415883223142", "channel_id": "1411240188641939588", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "第二波額外是莉莉帶三條\n這隊莉莉練度高就可以了\n莉莉要3啟或以上 及 靈塑5級或以上\n蘿坦要有+4\n\n莉莉一定要帶 扭曲雙子·白 跨越疼痛 35mm的魔法\n\n潘狄婭需要帶 永不停歇的演奏 回狂氣\n\n隊伍需要帶鑰令 腦中之音\n建議抓造物 遺落的祭祀刀 知無不言 恩賜之血 無名附肢 活性注射器 神經毒素\n\n如果隊友想補生存或傷害的話\n潘狄婭可以帶有暴擊傷害的命輪\n蘿坦可以帶切割與傷害\n法洛思可以帶有盾量加成的", "timestamp": "2025-08-30T07:57:06.260000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411240188641939588", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全4級400融災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1395992069688004689", "1181143392739147778"]}
